<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Drunkenness" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Drunkenness,</orth> 1) intoxication: <cit><quote>it hath pleased the devil d. to give place to the devil wrath,</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 2.3.297" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. II, 3, 297</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) addiction to drink: <cit><quote>d. is his best virtue,</quote> <bibl n="shak. aww 4.3.285" default="NO" valid="yes">All's IV, 3, 285</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. tn 2.5.81" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. II, 5, 81</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 3.4.389" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 4, 389</bibl>.
